#: ../../../driver-api/iio/hw-consumer.rst:3
msgid "HW consumer"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../driver-api/iio/hw-consumer.rst:4
msgid ""
"An IIO device can be directly connected to another device in hardware. In "
"this case the buffers between IIO provider and IIO consumer are handled by "
"hardware. The Industrial I/O HW consumer offers a way to bond these IIO "
"devices without software buffer for data. The implementation can be found "
"under :file:`drivers/iio/buffer/hw-consumer.c`"
msgstr ""

